      "explanation": "<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:624px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Exogenous causes</strong>(Iatrogenic)</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<ul>\n<li>Prolonged administration of glucocorticoids<strong> (the most common cause of Cushing\u2019s).</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>ACTH dependent</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<ul>\n<li>Cushing\u2019s disease: ACTH-secreting <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b775f0c475169277719593c573f6ff\">pituitary</span> adenoma( most common)</li>\n<li>Hypothalamic lesions</li>\n<li>Ectopic source - Neuroblastoma, Wilms tumor, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"2eaab075f416927771834adb276f1d\">Carcinoid</span> syndrome</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>ACTH independent</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<ul>\n<li>Adrenal adenoma/ carcinoma</li>\n<li>Pigmented <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"bfa856c77716927771939978c5afd0\">nodular</span> hyperplasia</li>\n<li>McCune Albright syndrome</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n\n\n<p style='font-size: 10px; color: #808080; font-style: italic;'></p>",
